<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Alarik Zekaiden</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-01-09 00:22:40</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I like this weapon because of it's solid damage/speed ratio, and it is easy to get earlier on (comparatively speaking), but that agility hit sure is nasty.  You end up having to get around 200pp worth of compensation jewelery and items to make up for it, or ignore it, and have a hard time running away from the average monster because you are slowed.  Good weapon, but a bad side-effect.</font></td></tr></table>
