<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Happy with my BBC</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-02-13 10:17:54</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This weapon rocks for a Dark Elf SK.  The speed/damage ratio is the best you're going to get through level 20.  That pesky AGI hit is easy to sqaush, just pick up a Gold Carnelian Wed. Ring (+5AGI) for about 25PP and an Onyx Earring (+2AGI) for 5PP and you're down to only -1AGI for a measly 30PP, what a deal!  :)  I actually have AGI stuff that gives me +12 total so I'm ahead of the game, best part is when I run from zone to zone I unequip it and the speed burst from +12AGI is like a SOW!  Woo-hoo! :)<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
