<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I just got my new BBC at level l5, and i must say at first i wasnt impressed, but after slashing constantly for 28-30 pts of dmg, and gettin critical hits from 50-96!!! i think its a great sword.  The AGI hit is realy harsh, but i pumped alot into my AGI specs anyway, and alot of my armor is able to give me AGI boosts.  Anyways, all in all with Double attack and a BBC i have found myself to be unstopable!  I even took out a Aviak Guard at leve l5!!! and was hunting cyclopses with my friends yesterday.</font></td></tr></table>
